They are as follows: (1) The arrangement of the Codex itself: In hoc codice continentur ueteris et noui testamenti Libri N LXXX13 Genesis ..... Malachias, Job, Thobias, Iudith, Hester, Erras (zEzra and Nehemiah), Machabeorum lib. duo. (2) The books according to the Hieronymian division. (3) The arrangement sicut diuidit sanctus Hilarus Romanae urbis antistes et Epiphanius Cyprius : Genesi . . . . Malachim qui et Angelus, Iob, Tobis, Hester, Iudith, Esdrae libri duo (Ezra and Nehemiah), Machabeorum libri duo (Studm Bz'hlim, ii, 290 ffi).
